|GKB-- Inferno ---------------------------------------------------|000

The ultimate violent expression of the Daloan current,
this invocation creates flame and heat of an intensity not
far removed from that inside of an active volcano.  All
living creatures except druids and their followers will
be badly burnt, and inanimate objects, whether on the
ground or carried by affected creatures, have a chance
of burning to ash.

